38140>>>>>                // If from main, this is a probably a main-file lookup from a Zoom
38140>>>>>                WebSet pbRender of oDetailButton to False
38141>>>>>                Case Break
38142>>>>>
38142>>>>>            Case Else 
38142>>>>>                // This may be the start of a drilldown query or this may be used for some kind of custom query.
38142>>>>>
38142>>>>>        Case End
38142>>>>>
38142>>>>>    End_Procedure
